Package com.aheaditec.wrapper.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CardConnection
    Implementation of this interface can be used to communicate with smartcard.
    CardReader
    Every reader type should implement this interface so they have unified API.
    InitStateListener
    Class wanting to use the Pairing should implement this listener to get Pairing object in case of successful initialization or ReaderInitException in case of failed initialization.
    OnAtrListener
    Listener for ATR response.
    OnBatteryLevelListener
    Listener for getBatteryLvl response.
    OnCardStateListener
    Listener for getCardState result.
    OnPairedReaderFoundListener
    Listener for scanForPairedReaders results.
    OnPairWithReaderListener
    Listener for pairWithReader result.
    OnSearchListener
    Listener for startSearching results.
    Pairing
    Classes implementing pairing with Bluetooth readers should implement this interface to keep track of pairing process.
    ReaderConnectionManager
    Every reader type should implement this interface so they have unified API.
    ReaderStatusListener
    Listener sending notifications about connection state.
